text><media:description type="plain"> Diana Ross attending the Metropolitan Museum of Art Costume Institute Benefit Gala 2025 in New York, in 2025. </media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260501-met-gala-diana-ross-gk-003082.jpg" height="1667" width="2500"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate><title>Your complete guide to the 2026 Met Gala</title><updateDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 09:00:00 GMT</updateDate></item><item><dc:creator>Yuliya Talmazan</dc:creator><dc:contributor>Charlene Gubash</dc:contributor><dateTimeWritten>Mon, 04 May 2026 08:45:25 GMT</dateTimeWritten><description>Iran warned the United States on Monday not to approach or enter the Strait of Hormuz as the American military launches a new effort to “guide” stranded ships through the critical waterway</description><expires>2112-01-01T00:00:00.000+0000</expires><guid>https://www.nbcnews.com/world/iran/iran-war-trump-mission-guide-ships-strait-hormuz-attack-energy-prices-rcna343406</guid><link>https://www.nbcnews.com/world/iran/iran-war-trump-mission-guide-ships-strait-hormuz-attack-energy-prices-rcna343406</link><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260504-hormuz-mb-0942-11f56d.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1667" width="2500"><media:credit>Reuters</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Ships and boats in the Strait of Hormuz, Musandam</media:text><media:description type="plain">Ships and boats in the Strait of Hormuz near Musandam, Oman, on May 1, 2026. </media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260504-trump-tehran-mb-0745-30a4d5.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1782" width="2500"><media:credit>Vahid Salemi</media:credit><media:text type="plain">Vehicles drive past a billboard with graphic showing Strait of Hormuz and sewn lips of President Trump in Tehran, Iran on May 2, 2026. </media:text><media:description type="plain">Vehicles pass a billboard in Tehran on Saturday which appears to show the sewn lips of Trump covered in a ribbon shaped to represent the Strait of Hormuz.</media:description></media:content><media:content url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260504-hormuz-mb-0845-125253.jpg" type="image/jpeg" medium="image" height="1666" width="2500"><media:credit>Indranil Aditya</media:credit><media:text type="plain">India Tanker Desh Garima Unloads Crude Amid Hormuz Supply Disruptions</media:text><media:description type="plain">India-flagged tanker Desh Garima unloads crude oil in Mumbai after transiting the Strait of Hormuz on April 30.</media:description></media:content><media:thumbnail url="https://media-cldnry.s-nbcnews.com/image/upload/t_fit_1500w/rockcms/2026-05/260504-hormuz-mb-0942-11f56d.jpg" height="1667" width="2500"></media:thumbnail><pubDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 08:45:25 GMT</pubDate><title>Iran threatens to attack U.S. forces in Strait of Hormuz after Trump launches mission to guide ships</title><updateDate>Mon, 04 May 2026 08:45:25 GMT</updateDate></item></channel></rss>